# conduit_proj — Cursor entrypoint

The source contract is `AGENTS.md` at the repo root. Read it first.
Everything below is Cursor-specific.

## Loop reminder

1. `gad snapshot --projectid conduit-proj`
2. Pick one task from `.planning/tasks/`
3. Implement
4. `gad tasks stamp <id> --projectid conduit-proj --status done --agent cursor --runtime cursor --skill <skill> --files <files>`
5. `gad state log "<delta>" --projectid conduit-proj`
6. Commit

## Cursor-specific notes

- Cursor's project chat reads this file. AGENTS.md has the full contract.
- Use `gad` CLI for planning mutations — never hand-edit XML under `.planning/`.
- Planning entity IDs: `CONDUIT-PROJ-D-<n>` decisions, `CONDUIT-PROJ-T-<phase>-<n>` tasks, `CONDUIT-PROJ-R-<n>` requirements.
